eb32ec14-2690-11b2-96de-a758c88947ba.title: so soft
eb32ec14-2690-11b2-96de-a758c88947ba.body: I love this shirt. Cloud knit fabric is what I want to live my life in. It is comfortable enough to lounge in but also very cute and I often wear it with jeans. I am petite and so the sleeves are definitely long on me, but not in a way that makes the shirt feel too big. The rest of the shirt is easy to adjust to fit a range of body shapes due to the wrap style! My bra size is pretty small and I often find wrap tops that gape too much, but I am still able to tighten this wrap to fit well.
eb32ec14-2690-11b2-96de-a758c88947ba.name: Allyson

eb32f59f-2690-11b2-9d96-0d7a374e7be8.title: Love the heavier cloudknit
eb32f59f-2690-11b2-9d96-0d7a374e7be8.body: Cloudknit is one of my favorite fabrics and having a heavier weight option is really great. I have both the oatmeal and the strawberry and they are in regular rotation for lounging around the house and staying the perfect temp! Looking forward to more styles in the heavyweight cloudknit
eb32f59f-2690-11b2-9d96-0d7a374e7be8.name: Natalie

eb32fea7-2690-11b2-99c3-b1434062b1f8.title: sleek & cozy
eb32fea7-2690-11b2-99c3-b1434062b1f8.body: I'm patiently waiting for these pants to go on sale this summer so I can buy another pair, but they just might not. The fit is incredibly flattering, the material is comfy for 60s-low 70s weather. It's definitely not the scuba-like, warmer frostknit fabric. I wouldn't consider this winter wear, but it's perfect for spring/fall.
eb32fea7-2690-11b2-99c3-b1434062b1f8.name: Cindy

eb335545-2690-11b2-8270-4f279ffefd84.title: Love this for running in the cold!
eb335545-2690-11b2-8270-4f279ffefd84.body: This fits great - I wore it in the snow during a long run and it kept me warm, not necessarily dry but it was great. There’s just enough room for another tight layer underneath. I have this in two colors now and the matching leggings, and the reflective material is great as well!
eb335545-2690-11b2-8270-4f279ffefd84.name: Mollie

eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.title: Amazing, cozy, must have!!
eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.body: I've been searching for the perfect, cozy pullover for the chillier months. This was PERFECT. It's much thicker and softer than the terry cotton crew neck, and also a much more relaxed fit. Ideal for workout pullover, yoga, pilates, or walks. I wanted something super oversized and slouchy, so I actually sized up quite a bit. But it's a must have, high recommend!
eb335d9d-2690-11b2-a782-fba9041d12cf.name: Ali

eb33657b-2690-11b2-bd20-192f02123ea0.title: LOVE IT
eb33657b-2690-11b2-bd20-192f02123ea0.body: SO CUTE!!!! i wear it with my court skirt for the cutest outfit!!! truly such a cute sweatshirt for sport lovers!!!
eb33657b-2690-11b2-bd20-192f02123ea0.name: Lauren

eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.title: favorite t-shirt
eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.body: I bought an extra size or two up so it would be a baggy fit on me. One of the most comfortable tshirts I've ever owned and it's so cute! It's my go to fave.
eb336c67-2690-11b2-823e-1557646b6571.name: Koty

eb3372b8-2690-11b2-bd83-a1db417e8389.title: So flattering!
eb3372b8-2690-11b2-bd83-a1db417e8389.body: This is the most comfortable I have ever felt in a tight fitting turtleneck! I love wearing it out and about under a sweater or on its own. The neck itself isn't too tight and the arms are the perfect length (take it from someone whose sleeves never go down to her wrists!). The only thing that might not be for everyone is how cropped it is but, with high waisted pants/leggings, or the confidence to show a little midriff, it works! Considering buying this in black I love it so!
eb3372b8-2690-11b2-bd83-a1db417e8389.name: Emma

eb33795a-2690-11b2-9c4d-9711a2449773.title: Please make in more colors
eb33795a-2690-11b2-9c4d-9711a2449773.body: The sea foam one is absolutely gorgeous. Y’all I’m pairing with a scort, bronzed make up and golden jewelry and I wear it out! I wish they would make so many colors so flattering
eb33795a-2690-11b2-9c4d-9711a2449773.name: Mary

eb337ffc-2690-11b2-97cc-cbb7c8b0571c.title: All good
eb337ffc-2690-11b2-97cc-cbb7c8b0571c.body: This is the warmest and coziest of all. I have the oatmeal color and wearing this fireside is what life is about 🙌🏼 it’s very soft and I love it
eb337ffc-2690-11b2-97cc-cbb7c8b0571c.name: Jenna

eb338826-2690-11b2-bba8-f301ee7ef3c5.title: Just right after sizing up
eb338826-2690-11b2-bba8-f301ee7ef3c5.body: Not too hot, not too cold - perfect for a winter run on top of a long sleeve! Fits snug without suffocating, although I did size up. The thick fabric feels sturdy but not stiff or plasticky. The single zipper pocket is great for my phone.
eb338826-2690-11b2-bba8-f301ee7ef3c5.name: Molly

eb338e54-2690-11b2-91cf-3f70bff11b56.title: Perfect base layer or on its own
eb338e54-2690-11b2-91cf-3f70bff11b56.body: This is so warm and great for layering, but it’s also thick and flattering enough to where if I get hot on my run I can wear it alone. I will get a lot of wear on this during the cold season!
eb338e54-2690-11b2-91cf-3f70bff11b56.name: Alyssa

eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.title: Best sweats
eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.body: I accidentally bought these in the wrong size and since they no longer have them in stock I gave them to my sister. It’s her second pair and she loves them! Please please bring these back in all the colors so that I can get another pair!
eb339596-2690-11b2-9906-cd87f5da47d4.name: Becky

eb339b5d-2690-11b2-8632-6b97240e9111.title: Comfiest top ever.
eb339b5d-2690-11b2-8632-6b97240e9111.body: This top is not only functional but super comfortable. The cloud knit material is my absolute favorite because it’s lightweight, breathable, and super soft. Definitely buying this in all of the other colors!
eb339b5d-2690-11b2-8632-6b97240e9111.name: Ana

eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.title: Softest
eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.body: Great sweats, the soft texture never fades
eb33a28b-2690-11b2-bb0f-83a206776a9a.name: Nadia

eb33a924-2690-11b2-a48e-db16f5ca1954.title: Fav Sweatshirt
eb33a924-2690-11b2-a48e-db16f5ca1954.body: I have these in both orange and blue/grey. I love the quality and oversized fit of this sweatshirt. It's my go to for cozy indoor or outdoor loungewear. I am 170 lb. with more of pear shape so I went for the Large and it has a oversized fit. I would love more colors!
eb33a924-2690-11b2-a48e-db16f5ca1954.name: Anne

eb33af85-2690-11b2-b6c1-3b8df09abe57.title: Staple for Comfy fit!
eb33af85-2690-11b2-b6c1-3b8df09abe57.body: These are very comfortable and flattering. I am tall and they aren't too short either. they are definitely more of a mid rise fit. I usually wear a small or medium in OV bottoms, I sized up and it was a good choice! I am 27in waist and 39in hips.
eb33af85-2690-11b2-b6c1-3b8df09abe57.name: Riley

eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.title: PHENOMENAL JACKET
eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.body: A breathable rainy day jacket, I bought a large so I could layer underneath as well! Used it in the winter snow! it kept me adequately warm and dry, the only down side was I didn’t realize I got snow in my pocket and went indoors and it melted. I didn’t know it was there until I reached into my pocket and there was a puddle of water. I learned to button it for next time. I love this jacket so much. Glad I made the investment it’s a great quality!
eb33b5d5-2690-11b2-a512-5faa7e99d024.name: Nayelly

eb33bc19-2690-11b2-91fe-f7c397a17e72.title: Comfiest ever!
eb33bc19-2690-11b2-91fe-f7c397a17e72.body: I needed a casual but cute fleece and this has just been the best. It's soft and warm and can be dressed up jeans or down with leggings or an exercise dress. The elastic at the bottom can be cinched if you want it and it looks so cute. I like the separate mini-pocket within the right pocket that I can put smaller items in. I sized up (5'10", normally a M but got a L) because I like an oversized fit, and it's great. I just roll up the sleeves which is super cute!
eb33bc19-2690-11b2-91fe-f7c397a17e72.name: Elizabeth

eb33c32d-2690-11b2-b743-81ad6dec8112.title: Adorable!
eb33c32d-2690-11b2-b743-81ad6dec8112.body: Can’t wait to match the kiddos in my life!
eb33c32d-2690-11b2-b743-81ad6dec8112.name: J.J.

eb33c918-2690-11b2-97aa-4bd1ef61e665.title: ☁️
eb33c918-2690-11b2-97aa-4bd1ef61e665.body: I’m not kidding when I say my kiddo hasn’t taken these off since he got them! They are so soft, a great fit (don’t wrinkle!) and it’s adorable seeing him wear OV. My son is about to turn 3 and the 3T fits perfectly!
eb33c918-2690-11b2-97aa-4bd1ef61e665.name: Karissa

eb33cf08-2690-11b2-8cef-efe86956492e.title: Super Super soft
eb33cf08-2690-11b2-8cef-efe86956492e.body: The coziest fabric that my daughter wants to live in. Perfect to wear home or while being active. Super lightweight and soft.
eb33cf08-2690-11b2-8cef-efe86956492e.name: Carly

eb33d69f-2690-11b2-bde5-f10b06e462b8.title: The coziest fabric
eb33d69f-2690-11b2-bde5-f10b06e462b8.body: So incredibly soft and cozy. Perfect for lounging at home or being active in. Like a second skin
eb33d69f-2690-11b2-bde5-f10b06e462b8.name: Carly
